data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom cottage-style home in the picturesque Village of Cobblestone located just a few minutes from downtown Woodstock, where you can explore a variety of shops, restaurants, and entertainment options. This location provides a perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility. Nestled in a peaceful community, this cottage style home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and timeless character. Upon entering, you'll step into a cozy and well-lit living space with an open layout, making it perfect for entertaining family and friends. This is an exceptional opportunity for those seeking a harmonious blend of comfort and timeless charm. Don't miss your chance to make this lovely residence your own and embrace the relaxed, village lifestyle it offers.
